Yeremia te nkaji o laitobirani loo motioo oo nkulupuok


1  Ele rorei ninye oewuo enetii Yeremia eing'uaa Olaitoriani ejo: 
2  “Tudumunye tadoi shomo enkaji o laitobirani loo ntokitin oo nkulupuok ore tene naaisho nanu iyie toning'o irorei laainei.” 
3  Nadoyio nanu alo enkaji o laitobirani loo ntokitin oo nkulupuok, ore teine neasisho ninye te nkeju enye engarri. 
4  Ore apa ina masaai naitobirita ninye te nkulukuoni nerruoyo te nkaina o laitobirani loo ntokitin oo nkulupuok, neitoki aitobir aitayunye enkae masaai, anaa enadol o laitobirani too ntokitin oo nkulupuok enaa enadol aa sidai te neas.


5  Neitoki ororei lo Laitoriani alotu enatii ejo: 
6  “Na aji e Israel, aimaidim nanu aikuna te intae anaa enaikuna ele aitobirani loo ntokitin oo nkulupuok? Olaitoriani ojo: ng'ura, ore anaa esarng'ab te nkaina o laitobirani loo ntokitin oo nkulupuok neijia itiuu intae te nkaina ai, na aji e Israel. 
7  Ore te pooki kata tenaibalunye tialo olosho aashu enkitoria, nchere kadotu nagil nainyal, 
8  naa ore ilo osho, laa tialo ninye airoro, teneibelekenya aing'uaa entorroni enye, nairridu ina torroni apa natejo kaitaas ninye. 
9  Naa ore te pooki kata tenaibalunye nanu tialo olosho aashu enkitoria nchere kashet naun ninye, 
10  naa teneas entorroni too nkonyek aainei, mening oltoilo lai, nairridu nanu teina sidai natejo pee aitaas ninye. 
11  Ore naa, tiaaki iltung'ana le Yuda o lelo oomanya Yerusalem: ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ng'ura, aitobirita entorroni tialo iyie naipiru enkitobirata tialo intae. Tushukunye, pooki ng'ae aing'uaa enkoitoi enye torrono, nintobiriri nkoitoi inyi o nkiaasin inyi.’


12  “Kake ejo ninche, ‘Pesho ina! Kisuj iyiook nkitobirat ang maate, neas pooki ng'ae te risioroto engolon oltau lenye torrono.’

Etanyaita iltung'ana Olaitoriani


13  “Neaku nji ejo Olaitoriani:

Nkilikuanu tiatua iloreren,

kaing'ae otoning'o enanyaanyukie ena?

Etaasa ina tito selenkei e Israel embae suuji oleng.


14  Kepal enturoto e Lebanon endapidapoi e Sirion?

Ketoyu nena ariak o ldoinyo naaimu lelo yerat ooirobi?


15  Kake maadamu nanu iltung'ana laainei,

epejoki ninche enkorropil nkaitin e lejare;

netarrorrote ninche tiatua nkoitoi enye,

too ilbaribarani musan,

neshomo aaim nkoitoi naangel

mme enkoitoi kitok,


16  eitaa enkop enye enaitureisho, entoki naing'asiakinie intarasi.

Ore pooki ng'ae oim embata neiputukuny neipirripir elukunya enye.


17  Anaa osiwuo ogol le nkilepunoto enkolong

kaidapash nanu ninche te dukuya olmang'atinta.

Kaisho nanu ninche oriong ai,

mme omom ai,

te nkolong enye o sina.”

Etarreshoki Yeremia pee eari metua


18  Nejo ninche, “Wootu, maitaikiti iyiook Yeremia irresheta, amu merruoyo enkitanapata to lapolosani, aashu enkiguana to lang'eni, aashu ororei to loiboni. Wootu, matar ninye to lng'ejep, nimikining iyiook hoo obo loo rorei lenyena.” 
19  Ng'uraki nanu Olaitoriani, nining olkiyioi lai. 
20  Kentorroni elakieki esidai? Ore eyia etuturutuo ninche engumoto tenkaraki enkishui ai. Tadamu ina naitasho te dukuya iyie pee airo esidai tenkaraki ninche, pee aibelekeny aiwuang'ie aitung'uaa ninche. 
21  Neaku iwa nkera enye meshomo aatum olameyu; nchooi ninche meshomo engolon empijan olalem, nchoo nkituaak enye eaku olupeno o nkolia. Metanang'are ilewa lenye keeya to lmeitai, metaari eleleroenye to lalem to larrabal. 
22  Metoning'ori olkiyioi eing'uaa nkajijik enye, tiniyau iyie lelo ooarr ninche metuata te luamata! Amu etuturutuo ninche engumoto pee aaya nanu, neirragakinye nkejek aainei irresheta. 
23  Ore eyia, iyiolo iyie Olaitoriani ilnukat lenye laarieki nanu matua. Mipalaki ninche entorroni enye, nimijut eng'oki enye too nkonyek inono. Nchoo ninche metanang'ari te dukuya iyie; ntaasa ninche te nkata engoro ino.

